TITLE: Defining BeforeFileProcessingEvent Class in TYPO3 CMS
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines the BeforeFileProcessingEvent class in TYPO3 CMS. It includes properties for the processing instruction, file object, and task type, along with getter and setter methods for these properties.
SOURCE: https://github.com/TYPO3-Documentation/TYPO3CMS-Reference-CoreApi/blob/main/Documentation/ApiOverview/Events/Events/Core/Resource/BeforeFileProcessingEvent.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: PHP
CODE:
```
final class BeforeFileProcessingEvent
{
    private ProcessingInstruction $instruction;
    private FileInterface $file;
    private string $taskType;

    public function __construct(ProcessingInstruction $instruction, FileInterface $file, string $taskType)
    {
        $this->instruction = $instruction;
        $this->file = $file;
        $this->taskType = $taskType;
    }

    public function getInstruction(): ProcessingInstruction
    {
        return $this->instruction;
    }

    public function getFile(): FileInterface
    {
        return $this->file;
    }

    public function getTaskType(): string
    {
        return $this->taskType;
    }

    public function setFile(FileInterface $file): void
    {
