TITLE: Github Actions Workflow Configuration for TYPO3 Styleguide (YAML)
DESCRIPTION: YAML configuration for Github Actions CI/CD pipeline that automates testing for the TYPO3 Styleguide extension. It defines jobs that run on push, pull request, and daily schedule, executing composer validation, PHP linting, coding guidelines checks, PHPStan analysis, unit tests, and functional tests with multiple database systems.
