TITLE: Implementing Cache Usage in TYPO3 PHP Class
DESCRIPTION: Example class demonstrating cache injection and usage with get/set operations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/TYPO3-Documentation/TYPO3CMS-Reference-CoreApi/blob/main/Documentation/ApiOverview/CachingFramework/Developer/Index.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
namespace MyVendor\MyExtension;

use TYPO3\CMS\Core\Cache\Frontend\FrontendInterface;

class MyClass
{
    protected FrontendInterface $cache;

    public function __construct(FrontendInterface $cache)
    {
        $this->cache = $cache;
    }

    public function getResults(): array
    {
        $cacheIdentifier = 'myext_calculate_something';
        $result = $this->cache->get($cacheIdentifier);
        if ($result === false) {
            $result = $this->calculateExpensiveOperation();
            $this->cache->set($cacheIdentifier, $result);
        }
        return $result;
    }
```

