TITLE: Implementing BeforeTcaOverridesEvent Listener in TYPO3 PHP
DESCRIPTION: Example of an event listener implementation for the BeforeTcaOverridesEvent in TYPO3. This allows dynamically generating TCA before TCA overrides are applied, which is useful for TCA generator extensions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/TYPO3-Documentation/TYPO3CMS-Reference-CoreApi/blob/main/Documentation/ApiOverview/Events/Events/Core/Configuration/BeforeTcaOverridesEvent.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace MyVendor\MyExtension\Configuration\EventListener;

use TYPO3\CMS\Core\Configuration\Event\BeforeTcaOverridesEvent;

final class MyEventListener
{
    public function __invoke(BeforeTcaOverridesEvent $event): void
    {
        // Get current TCA
        $tca = $event->getTca();

        // Add dynamic base TCA for my specific thing, here using a
        // dedicated custom helper to add dynamic pages TCA
        $tca = $this->addDynamicBaseTca($tca);

        // Set changed TCA
        $event->setTca($tca);
    }

    private function addDynamicBaseTca(array $tca): array
    {
        // Do your thing here
        return $tca;
    }
}
```

