SOURCE: https://github.com/TYPO3-Documentation/TYPO3CMS-Reference-CoreApi/blob/main/Documentation/ExtensionArchitecture/HowTo/BackendModule/_ModuleConfiguration/_AdminModuleControllerDebugAction.rst.txt#2025-04-16_snippet_0

