TITLE: Version-Compatible Middleware Registration for TYPO3 v12 and v13
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to register a Doctrine DBAL driver middleware that works in both TYPO3 v12 and v13 using version checking.
SOURCE: https://github.com/TYPO3-Documentation/TYPO3CMS-Reference-CoreApi/blob/main/Documentation/ApiOverview/Database/Middleware/Index.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use TYPO3\CMS\Core\Information\Typo3Version;

if ((new Typo3Version())->getMajorVersion() < 13) {
    // Configuration for TYPO3 v12
    $GLOBALS['TYPO3_CONF_VARS']['DB']['Connections']['Default']['driverMiddlewares'] = array_merge(
        $GLOBALS['TYPO3_CONF_VARS']['DB']['Connections']['Default']['driverMiddlewares'] ?? [],
        [
            'my-middleware' => \Vendor\Extension\Driver\MyDriverMiddleware::class,
        ]
    );
} else {
    // Configuration for TYPO3 v13
    $GLOBALS['TYPO3_CONF_VARS']['DB']['Connections']['Default']['middlewares'] = array_merge(
        $GLOBALS['TYPO3_CONF_VARS']['DB']['Connections']['Default']['middlewares'] ?? [],
        [
            'my-middleware' => [
                'target' => \Vendor\Extension\Driver\MyDriverMiddleware::class,
                'after' => ['typo3/core/custom-platform-driver-middleware'],
            ],
        ]
    );
}
```

