TITLE: Configuring TYPO3 Application Context in Apache
DESCRIPTION: Apache configuration examples showing how to set TYPO3 application contexts either using a static value or dynamically based on host headers using mod_rewrite or setenvif modules.
SOURCE: https://github.com/TYPO3-Documentation/TYPO3CMS-Reference-CoreApi/blob/main/Documentation/ApiOverview/RequestLifeCycle/Bootstrapping.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_2

