LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
public function canHandleLink(array $linkParts): bool
{
    if (!$linkParts['url'] instanceof LinkService) {
        return false;
    }
    $data = $linkParts['url']->getData();
    if (!isset($data['type']) || $data['type'] !== 'github') {
        return false;
    }
    $this->linkParts = $linkParts;
    return true;
}
```

