SOURCE: https://github.com/TYPO3-Documentation/TYPO3CMS-Reference-CoreApi/blob/main/Documentation/ApiOverview/Events/Events/Core/Resource/AfterDefaultUploadFolderWasResolvedEvent.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_0

