TITLE: Implementing DeferredAction with RequireJS in TYPO3 Notification API
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to implement a DeferredAction in the TYPO3 Notification API using RequireJS for compatibility with TYPO3 v11. The action performs an AJAX request that returns a Promise.
SOURCE: https://github.com/TYPO3-Documentation/TYPO3CMS-Reference-CoreApi/blob/main/Documentation/ApiOverview/FlashMessages/NotificationApi.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
