TITLE: JavaScript Custom Link Handler Implementation
DESCRIPTION: JavaScript code for handling link creation in the custom link browser tab.
SOURCE: https://github.com/TYPO3-Documentation/TYPO3CMS-Reference-CoreApi/blob/main/Documentation/ApiOverview/LinkHandling/Tutorials/CustomLinkBrowser.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
class CustomLinkHandler {
    constructor() {
        this.linkBrowser = window.TYPO3.LinkBrowser;
    }

    /**
     * @param {string} value
     */
    setLink(value) {
        const issueId = document.querySelector('[name="issue"]').value;
        const baseUrl = 'github';

        this.linkBrowser.finalizeFunction('t3://' + baseUrl + '?issue=' + issueId);
    }
}

export default new CustomLinkHandler();
```

