DESCRIPTION: PHP code demonstrating how to implement a PageTree helper class for TYPO3 acceptance tests.
SOURCE: https://github.com/TYPO3-Documentation/TYPO3CMS-Reference-CoreApi/blob/main/Documentation/Testing/AcceptanceTesting/Index.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
namespace TYPO3\TestingFramework\Core\Acceptance\Support\Helper;

use Facebook\WebDriver\Remote\RemoteWebElement;
use TYPO3\TestingFramework\Core\Acceptance\Step\Backend\Admin;

class PageTree extends Admin implements PageTreeInterface
{
    public function getPageXpath(string $pageName, int $level = 1): string
    {
        return '//*[contains(@class, "treelist-wrapper")]'
            . '//*[contains(@class, "treelist-collapse-wrapper")]'
            . '/ol[2]/li[contains(@class, "treelist-level-' . $level . '")]'
            . '/div/span[contains(text(), "' . $pageName . '")]';
    }
}
```

