CODE:
```
public function process(ServerRequestInterface $request, RequestHandlerInterface $handler): ResponseInterface
{
    $jsonResponse = ['seasons' => $this->getSeasons($request)];
    $body = $this->streamFactory->createStream(json_encode($jsonResponse));
