TITLE: Implementing ModifyImageManipulationPreviewUrlEvent Listener in TYPO3
DESCRIPTION: Example implementation of an event listener for ModifyImageManipulationPreviewUrlEvent that modifies the preview URL for image manipulation elements. The event listener demonstrates how to set a custom preview URL based on file properties and configuration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/TYPO3-Documentation/TYPO3CMS-Reference-CoreApi/blob/main/Documentation/ApiOverview/Events/Events/Backend/ModifyImageManipulationPreviewUrlEvent.rst#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace MyVendor\MyExtension\Backend\EventListener;

use TYPO3\CMS\Backend\Form\Event\ModifyImageManipulationPreviewUrlEvent;

final class MyEventListener
{
    public function __invoke(ModifyImageManipulationPreviewUrlEvent $event): void
    {
        // Only set preview URL for specific tables and fields
        if ($event->getTable() !== 'sys_file_reference'
            || $event->getField() !== 'crop'
        ) {
            return;
        }

        $file = $event->getFile();
        if ($file === null) {
            return;
        }

        // Set preview URL based on custom logic
        $previewUrl = sprintf(
            'https://example.org/preview/%d',
            $file->getUid()
        );
        $event->setPreviewUrl($previewUrl);
    }
}

```

